#### Using Cloud Foundry CLI

Run `cf marketplace -s <%= service_version -%>`. This will display
information about each service plan offered by the Crunchy
service. Choose the plan that best fits your application requirements.

#### Using Pivotal Apps Manager

1. Select **Marketplace** on the left navigation menu.
1. Find and select **Crunchy PostgreSQL** in the list of available services.
1. Browse the available service plans and choose the one that best fits your application requirements.
